Mail-Webmail-Gmail version 1.00
===============================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

lib qw(lib)
LWP::UserAgent
HTTP::Headers
HTTP::Cookies
HTTP::Request::Common
Crypt::SSLeay
Exporter

